		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Sharing stories help people get to know each other better and creates a collaborative atmosphere. It provides local knowledge for resilience planning. It prompts discussion about how people experience hazards in different ways and why this might be so.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
